  "title": "Business Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Company</strong><br>\nOur client is a growing consultancy firm delivering tailored business solutions across diverse industries. To support their expansion, they are seeking motivated and results-driven <strong>Business Consultants</strong> with established networks to help drive new client acquisition.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Generate new business opportunities by tapping into personal and professional networks.</li>\n  <li>Promote and represent the firm’s consultancy services to potential clients.</li>\n  <li>Manage the full sales cycle: prospecting, pitching, negotiation, and deal closure.</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain long-term client relationships to drive repeat business.</li>\n  <li>Stay informed on market trends and industry developments to identify opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven track record in sales, business development, or consultancy.</li>\n  <li>Existing client network or leads to leverage.</li>\n  <li>Entrepreneurial and self-motivated, able to work independently.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Results-oriented with strong drive to achieve targets.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What’s on Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fully commission-based role with <strong>high earning potential</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Autonomy to manage your own clients and portfolio.</li>\n  <li>Opportunity to be part of a dynamic and growing consultancy firm.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We value every application, but only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you for considering this opportunity!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
